descriptionHtml:
its Preset for chargen
how to install :
1.Download preset file.
2. put preset file (14.slot) into u skyrim folder ( skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\Chargen\presets )
3. launch skyrim and load any working safe game.
4.type into console showracemenu
5.choice race redguard and load preset from slot 14.
